description:
Beauty legend (and Jess's former boss!) Jane Larkworthy dishes on being the beauty director at W and Jane magazines, the rise of "influencers," and the odor-fighting powers of chlorophyll. We also get into hair accessories for grown ups, natural beauty at Nordstrom, and nipple reduction surgery.
